title: Pictures: Oktoberfest in Germany
text:
Caption Oktoberfest 2015 Matthias Schrader / Associated Press 
A young woman celebrates the opening of the 182. Oktoberfest beer festival in Munich, southern Germany, Saturday, Sept. 19, 2015. The world's largest beer festival will be held from Sept. 19 to Oct. 4, 2015. 
A young woman celebrates the opening of the 182. Oktoberfest beer festival in Munich, southern Germany, Saturday, Sept. 19, 2015. The world's largest beer festival will be held from Sept. 19 to Oct. 4, 2015. (Matthias Schrader / Associated Press) Caption Oktoberfest 2015 Alexander Hassenstein / Getty Images 
Munich Mayor Dieter Reiter pounds a tap into the first Oktoberfest beer barrel at the Schottenhamel beer tent on the opening day of the 2015 Oktoberfest on Sept. 19, 2015 in Munich, Germany. The 182nd Oktoberfest runs through Oct. 4 and will draw millions of visitors from across the globe for the world's largest beer fest. 
Munich Mayor Dieter Reiter pounds a tap into the first Oktoberfest beer barrel at the Schottenhamel beer tent on the opening day of the 2015 Oktoberfest on Sept. 19, 2015 in Munich, Germany. The 182nd Oktoberfest runs through Oct. 4 and will draw millions of visitors from across the globe for the world's largest beer fest. (Alexander Hassenstein / Getty Images)
